<h1>Angular 19 Course by Tech Sharmit</h1>

<h2>Date Pipe in Angular with ShortDate, MediumDate and LongDate </h2>

<p>
    Current Date (Without Date Pipe) : {{CurrentDate}}
</p>

<p>
    Current Date (with Date Pipe - shortdate) : {{CurrentDate | date : 'shortDate'}}
    <br> Current Date (with Date Pipe - short) : {{CurrentDate | date : 'short'}}
</p>

<p>
    Current Date (with Date Pipe - MediumDate) : {{CurrentDate | date : 'mediumDate'}}
    <br> Current Date (with Date Pipe - medium) : {{CurrentDate | date : 'medium'}}

</p>

<p>
    Current Date (with Date Pipe - LongDate) : {{CurrentDate | date : 'longDate'}}
    <br> Current Date (with Date Pipe - long) : {{CurrentDate | date : 'long'}}

</p>
